<h4>OVER THE COUNTER (OTC) ITEMS AVAILABLE</h4>
<h4>AT THE STUDENT HEALTH CENTER PHARMACY</h4>
<p>The BYU-Idaho Student Health Center Pharmacy carries a wide variety of over-the-counter products at affordable prices, available without a prescription to meet your healthcare needs.</p>
<p>We carry a wide variety of diabetic supplies, including:</p>
<ul>
<li style="list-style: square; margin-left: 50px;">Test strips, Syringes &amp; Lancets</li>
</ul>
<p>Most of which are covered by private insurance if you get a prescription from your physician.</p>
<p><strong>We also carry the following valuable kits:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>First Aid to Go!&reg;: <strong>$1.00!</strong><br /><span class="comment"><span class="comment">a 12 item portable first aid kit</span></span>
<div>perfect for backpacks</div>
</li>
<li>First Aid Essentials: <strong>$6.50</strong> <br /><span class="comment"><span class="comment">a 131 piece first aid kit perfect</span></span>
<div>for dorm rooms, apartments, or automobiles</div>
</li>
<li>Healthy Traveler Kit - International: <strong>$17.00</strong> <br /><span class="comment"><span class="comment">Filled with valuable bandages and medications perfect</span></span>
<div>for those traveling overseas</div>
</li>
<li>Healthy Traveler Kit - Domestic: <strong>$12.50</strong> <br /><span class="comment"><span class="comment">A modified version of our international kit with less items yet still valuable</span></span>
<div>for any travel within the U.S.</div>
</li>
<li>Flu Survival Kit: <strong>$5.00</strong> <br /><span class="comment"><span class="comment">An inexpensive kit designed to help treat flu and flu-like symptoms as well as protect you from infection or infecting others</span></span>
<div>for details, see <a href="x45841.xml">Cough, Cold, and Flu</a></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
